1. The event is triggered with a mouse click
2. When the mouse is clicked, a new coin entity spawns on the map. it should be noted that the coin only spawns when there are no obstacles 
in its position.
3. The coin affects all dudes in the world as all of the dudes focus on trying to catch the coin.
4. The new entity is a bitcoin that has an animation that rotates itself and stays in plays until a dude is adjacent to it and then it is removed from the world.
